race.comment: Competitive contest. ROWEINER'S DANCE (2) absolutely loves this course and distance with 11 wins and three placings from 17 attempts and has won three from five when first-up. Should be able to push forward from the middle draw and will give backers a sight. SATURDAY VIBES (9) has hit the frame at his past four outings and looks to be building up to another victory. Don't dismiss lightly. FAMILY STAR (5) is a ten-time winner here on his home circuit who maps ideally for this from gate two. In the mix. MOLONGLE SURPRISE (3) has been in the market at his last couple of starts but hasn't made an impression. Next in line from the inside alley.
